data.description: Sought after 2 Story, Brick constructed, Stand-Alone home in a gated community. Located on a Corner w/Lots of windows-great natural lighting in Gated Community called Midtown Village of popular EaDo. 2 Bedrooms, 2 baths * a large game room downstairs that also could be used as a home office or 3rd bedroom. Upgrades include tasteful tile flooring in guest bedroom, recessed lighting w/raised ceilings, dining room + stairs. Light and bright living room w/recessed lighting, Kitchen with granite, NEW electric range and wood cabinetry. All appliances stay + wine fridge. Spacious primary & immaculate bath w/separate shower. 2 vanities & deep soaking tub. Also, private fenced outdoor space! Instant access to the Astros Stadium, BBVA Stadium & DT to mention a few.  Lock, and leave living. Lowest price in the Community of its size. PAINT AND CARPET
